column.name: user_id
column.Comment: Id of the user record in INT_USERS table

column.name: alias
column.Comment: EVAM alias that will be used during login etc.

column.name: password
column.Comment: User's current password in encrypted format

column.name: password2
column.Comment: User's last password in encrypted format. For security controls

column.name: password3
column.Comment: User's oldest password recorded in encrypted format.

column.name: profile_id
column.Comment: user's profile id. Mandatory and FK to INT_USER_PROFILE

column.name: is_logged_in
column.Comment: flag to check user login status into EVAM Environment.
